title: [BUG]Empty UI
body:

### Describe the problem

### Code to reproduce issue

### Other info / logs
Include any logs or source code that would be helpful to diagnose the problem. If including tracebacks,
please include the full traceback. Large logs and files should be attached.

Hi everyone, I get another question.
After running several runs, I start tracking UI by CMD command 'mlflow ui', and then 'http://localhost:5000'. I can get into the UI inference, but it's empty, there is nothing, which is shown below:
![untitled](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/60772001/74102858-527d5a80-4b82-11ea-8410-1c9ccc2a6785.png)

Does anyone have similar issues?
